    {
      "@id": "source-doc:e7713be25757d91286a1:span-1",
      "@type": "TextSpan",
      "text": "We partnered with artists, designers, and builders to create new AI tools that solve real problems in their creative workflows.Here’s what’s new:— Introducing Google Pics in @GoogleWorkspace: A brand-new image creation & editing tool. Move and resize objects, add text, and translate just by hovering and clicking— Big updates to @GoogleFlow: 1) You can now create with Gemini Omni Flash in Google Flow 2) Google Flow Agent is a multi-step creative partner that reasons and plans complex tasks with you.",
